*
         * @prop {String|undefined} addressBookMode
         * @description
         *   The current address book mode or undefined if the address book is not activated.

*
         * @prop {Object|undefined} addressBookOptions
         * @description
         *   The current address book options (e.g. type: 'Email' or 'SMS', recipient field, s.o.).

*
                 * @event custom-event
                 * @param {String=open-address-book} eventName
                 * @param {Object} data Address book values.
                 * @param {String} data.type Type of the address book.
                 * @param {String} data.addressBookTitle Optional address book title
                 *  for (e.g. customer user selection instead of recipients).
                 * @param {Boolean} data.multipleSelection Whether the address book supports multiple selection or not.
                 * @param {String} data.selectionOptionLabelKey Key which is used to select entries.
                 * @param {String} data.fieldName Name of the field that triggers this event.
                 * @param {String} data.fieldLabel Label of the field that triggers this event.
                 * @param {Array} data.fieldLocalLabelPlaceholder LocalLabelPlaceholder of the field that
                 *  triggers this event (placeholder already translated).
                 * @param {Array|String} data.currentValue Current value of the field that triggers this event.
                 * @param {Array} data.currentOptions Current options of the address book defined for the field.
                 * @param {Array} data.connectedSelectedRecipientValues Currently selected recipients in connected
                 *  fields.
                 * @description
                 *   Raised when the address book button is clicked in the `inline-action` mode.
